{"type":"article","id":22593,"title":"[多图]《逆统战：致地与海的革命者》桌游介绍，如内容与现实有雷同不是巧合，各位要选择哪个阵营?","uid":21307,"topics":[17,16,161],"contents":"你如果有买的意愿的话请填一下这个問卷&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.surveycake.com/s/P4qny\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.surveycake.com/s/P4qny</a><br>\n沒要買的可以募資<br>\n<a href=\"https://linktr.ee/ReversedFront\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://linktr.ee/ReversedFront</a><br>\n<br>\n台湾新出的桌游分为九个阵营:<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/nAQlOG6.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/nAQlOG6.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/nAQlOG6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n✧ 游戏世界观 — — 东方大陆（The Cathaian Continent）的七十年战争<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/fbBjxMf.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/fbBjxMf.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/fbBjxMf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n香港（Hong Kong） — — 1997年沦陷<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/yBhI1mm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/yBhI1mm.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/yBhI1mm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n蒙古（Mongolia） — — 1966年半壁沦陷<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/pCUfr7L.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/pCUfr7L.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/pCUfr7L.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n藏國（Tibet） — — 1959年淪陷<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/EvLqf1K.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/EvLqf1K.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/EvLqf1K.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n哈萨克（Kazakhia） — — 1951年战败<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/7q225bG.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/7q225bG.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/7q225bG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n维吾尔（Uyghuria） — — 1949年沦陷<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/UZEn3Zl.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UZEn3Zl.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/UZEn3Zl.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n满洲（Manchuria） — — 1945年沦陷<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/1If0JXL.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1If0JXL.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/1If0JXL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n台湾（Taiwan） — — 尚未沦陷的海邦<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/6ZjtcXB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/6ZjtcXB.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/6ZjtcXB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>以及各位来自墙内的葱油们</b><br>\n<br>\n反贼（Rebels） — — 隐身中华的反逆者<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/nMRYLFg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/nMRYLFg.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/nMRYLFg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/GgoPGs0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/GgoPGs0.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/GgoPGs0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n以及以上这些的敌对方，邪恶中共<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/r85QM9d.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/r85QM9d.jpg\" alt=\"https://imgur.com/r85QM9d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n.<br>\n.<br>\n.<br>\n.<br>\n.<br>\n详细网址请上:<br>\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@reversedfront/%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%B1%E5%8F%B2%E8%A9%A9%E6%A1%8C%E9%81%8A-%E9%80%86%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B0-%E8%87%B4%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%87%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E8%80%85-%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9-1a70f9d66c75\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@reversedfront/%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%B1%E5%8F%B2%E8%A9%A9%E6%A1%8C%E9%81%8A-%E9%